_sText:
To install:
extract the file into your maps folder.
maps folder location:
programs->steam->steamapps->"your username"->Counter-Strike Source->cstrike->maps.

all credits goes to me, Robert Handley AND of course the originall creator of GG_Deagle. If you are going to use it to make a remake of it, or use it in your mod or in anything else, you have to put me into the credits, or else the evil monkey will facerape you!
